name: 劳伦·马赫 Lauren Maher
intro: Mini Bio (1)　　Lauren Maher was born as Lauren Robinson Maher. She is known for her work on Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest (2006), Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End (2007) and Coherence (2013).　　Trivia (4)　　Speaks Italian.　　Graduated with a degree in theatre arts from Marymount Manhattan College in New York City.　　Studied theatre in London at Richmond College.　　Born in Boynton Beach, Florida.
